# houston

### Instance type

- Provider: On premise
- Instance type:
  [NiPoGi E3B](https://www.minimachines.net/actu/nipogi-e3b-un-minipc-ryzen-5-7430u-16-512-go-a-299e-133317)
- CPU: 6 cores (12 threads)
- RAM: 16 GB
- Storage: 512 GB SSD

### Services

- kandim (identity management platform)

## Initial deployment

Add new machine

```bash
just machine-add houston
```

Get Device ID and edit `machines/houston/configuration.nix` and change host IP and
installation disk destination `disko.devices.disk.main.device` (ex:
`/dev/disk/by-id/xxx` or `/dev/sda`)

```bash
just machine-get-disk-id 192.168.254.137
```

Boot on the clan USB key

```bash
clan machines install houston --target-host 192.168.254.137 --update-hardware-config nixos-facter
```

## Update deployment

Update host installation

```bash
clan machines update houston
```
